    "body": "@Carreau OK you are probably going to wake up in a few hours.  I have a few more before I crash.  When I was working on this branch, I broke the hiding/showing of the cell toolbars.  The reason is that i had to create a ctb_wrapper div that has an hbox class.  Because of this I can't just add and remove the `display: block` as you were doing before.\n\nBut more importantly, I realized that the current design couples the management of all of the CellToolbars into the class itself.  The problem is that it means people can't easily create cells by hand and show/hide the celltoolbar on a per cell basis.  We don't need to do that, but I can easily imagine people who might want to do this.  Let's maybe try to IRC about this tomorrow.\n"
  },
