    "body": "@Carreau OK I am done with this work.  Please look carefully at what I did.  There is still one problem: all celltoolbar instances have to have the same preset active.  But let's merge this and worry about that later if people need it.\n\nOne thing we need to be very careful about is decoupling our classes.  For example, you had the creation of the select UI for the main toolbar as a class attributed of CellToolbar.  That made it difficult to change the UI for preset selection when cells are used on other web pages.  Have a look at how I decoupled these things - I used events and a new list_presets method.\n\nBut this branch should be ready to merge after you double check everything.\n"
  },
